        Constructor to build an instance of User, not null variables are password, forename, surname, email address and if the User is an Employee.
        Parameters:
        pwd - : String of the password of the user.
        foreName - : String of the user's forename.
        surName - : String of the user's surname.
        email - : String of the User's email.
        emp - : Boolean to determine if the User is an Employee or not.
